# Local/private project notes and generated site drafts.
#
# `docs/` is mostly internal (SESSION notes, design briefs, internal
# audits, content with personal infra refs). We ignore the directory by
# default and explicitly track just the user-facing pages with `!`
# below. If you add a new public doc, add an exception here.
docs/*
!docs/README.md
!docs/GETTING-STARTED.md
!docs/DEPLOY.md
!docs/bug-reports/
audit/
onepage/
ABOUT.md
ABOUT-companion.md
CLAUDE.md
MIGRATION.md
MORNING-SUMMARY.md
# Legacy branding from the previous project name (Nautilus → Odysseus).
nautilus.png

# Local SQLite history file created when running api.py outside Docker
# (e.g. for compile checks or dev shells). In the container it lives at
# /app/data/odysseus.db — irrelevant to the repo.
scripts/odysseus.db
scripts/odysseus.db-*
default.profraw
